('96094','33149','5','Modern designer villa in Sineu for sale'),
('96095','33150','5','The owner, an architect from Austria, has planned and created this modern villa with exquisite and high quality materials. It stands on a flat, approx 15,000m² of land. A massive wooden door leads into the covered gravel courtyard, called the Patio. The approx 300m² of living space spread over living-dining room, modern fitted kitchen, utility room, guest toilet, 2 guest bedrooms with en suite bathroom and the master bedroom with walk-in dressing room and bathroom en suite. From the roof terrace you have a beautiful panoramic view. The fine facilities includes among others air conditioning h / c, panoramic window with sliding panels, fireplace in the living room, elegant handmade furniture etc. You can relax at the 60m² large pool, surrounded by sun terraces. Water from our own source feeds not only the pool but also the entire house and the garden'),
